      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">真的太特么好看了，让人忍不住立即找出雷乃的电影再看一遍。“和你一样，我也曾经试图竭尽全力同遗忘作斗争。和你一样，我忘记了一切。和你一样，我曾经渴望拥有一段难以慰藉的回忆，一段对影子和碑石的回忆。”</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1400707/?comment_id=3960497845"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="3956213343">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-3956213343" class="vote-count">0</span>
              <a id="btn-3956213343" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="3956213343">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/194525076/">那海加得呐</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/3956213343">2023-10-08 15:03:48</a>
          <span class="comment-location">北京</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">五星给那流水般的文字。用最庸俗的故事和桥段写出了最永恒的爱情和最深刻的对战争的反思。</span>
      </p>
